\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you give me your full name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Elsie Brodney Baker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And your present address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 15 Addison Court, Addison Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You're unmarried?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your date of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 October the eighteenth - ninety-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Eleven Cooper Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well it was my home from then - from the time I was born - until 1965, it would be, wouldn't it. That was our home - yes - that was our home - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you say that that had a district name or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 The whole of this district was Charlotteville. It was Charlotteville - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So your family didn't move?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No. My father and mother went there - at least my father - think he was there before he was married - just before. They lived - they went there when they were married and - er - my father died back in 1923 and my mother died in 1948. So they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So they always lived in the same house after they were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Two sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And where did you come in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 First.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many years between you and your next sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Um - just over three between myself and my next sister and then there's two years between those two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - I should think he would be about thirty-eight - thirty-seven - thirty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Guildford. He was born - his - his home was down a passageway by the old blacksmiths shop - I don't know if you ever knew the old blac
ksmiths shop in the High Street. Um - well, you know where Grimmonds shop was - and - er - do you remember Limpus's the milk people - well opposite there was the blacksmiths shop.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There was a - yes - I didn't know it because my grandparents died bef
ore he married you see and that was when he went to live in our house. Er - that's where he was born as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 He was a carriage builder for May and Jacobs. Mem. All his life - well all his working life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What sort of carriages did they make?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 All sorts of carriages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would that include motor cars?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, no, no. He was made redundant at sixty and - er - the cars came in. These were horse drawn carriages - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 This was in Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Where the Municipal buildings are now - it was a big shop front there with the carriages in and that sort of thing. He went there at fourteen and he worked 'til sixty and then he was redundant and in those days of course there was no pay. No redundancy - 
no nothing. It was hard on him - yes. And on my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did he ever have another job before or after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, no, went straight there at fourteen - he was apprenticed at fourteen and worked til he was sixty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So that was all his working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did he do any casual or part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Did he? No. He had his allotment up here on Pewley Way which was his hobby. That was only his hobby. No he didn't do any - no. No, he more or less broke up after he - they - well you know - you know what a man is when - er - the work stops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Apart from the time when he had to retire because of being redundant do you ever remember him being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well - my mother was nine
 years younger than my father - and I suppose - I think she was about twenty-nine when she was married and I was born about eighteen months after they were - er - married - so she'd be thirty to thirty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - Shrewsbury - just outside Shrewsbury.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Had she any jobs before she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, she again was in domestic service. Hereabouts, where she met my father, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she work after she was married or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well she did when my father's work s
topped and there was nothing - she did - er - nursing. She wasn't a trained nurse but she was a born nurse and she used to do - er - night nursing and - er - and go out at night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That was much later - earlier on when you were at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh, no, n
o. Oh, no, she didn't - of course I'm forgetting it's up to 1918 sort of thing. Oh no, she didn't - she didn't work until after - well after - no I don't think she did after his - I can't remember what she did after his - er - work stopped - you know - I 
can't - because I then - probably was at......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But when you were young and at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, she never worked - oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not even part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, gracious no. She had three children and she had enough to do at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many rooms were there in the house at Cooper Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Six rooms, six nice rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And can you describe the house to me - downstairs what would it be like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, there were two sitting rooms and - er - we used to call it a scullery in those days, you know
, and - er - two were quite nice and very high ceilinged - it's on the top of a hill and - er - nice high rooms - plenty of room and - er - three bedrooms upstairs - my father and mother had one - my two sisters had one and I had the third one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did anyone else besides your parents and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No relatives or lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. At home, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My mother did the sewing and my father mended our shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were the clothes always made by your mother - were they sometimes bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When we got about twelve - or twelve to fourteen, sort of thing
, she got a dressmaker to do the top - you know - the coats and things - but she made all our other things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever have any second hand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about shoes - would they be bought at a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, yes, oh yes, we lived as .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And then your father did the repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh he did all the repairing but we bought the shoes - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I can't tell you - I expect he did. I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember him doing anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
I expect he did the washing up and - I know when she was not well he looked after us and that sort of thing - but I mean as regards doing jobs in the house well I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would he do the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No. Um - in those days I think we used to have the inside decorated - but he didn't do it - I mean they had to pay for it but he didn't do it - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about repairs to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well that was supposed to be the landlords - er - pigeon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And improvements to the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They never did any. They still haven't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember if your father ever dressed or undressed you or bathed you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I don't remember - but I think he did when we were quite small - yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember him reading to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
I expect so - because he was a great reader. I don't - can't recall anything particular. I expect he did - he was very fond of his children - I mean nothing was too - great and ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think he told you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember if he ever took you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so - we used to go out together when we did go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would he look after you when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think she - don't think she ever went out much like that - but - er - he naturally would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But he did when she was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, he naturally would look after us then - if she went out but - er - I doubt if she ever went out on her own then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh well, we used to sort of do the washing up and help make the beds and ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 These were regular things you were expected to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, we were expected to do little odds and ends in the house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you continue to do these tasks after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, after I - soon after I left school I was away from home - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about your sisters, you don't remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect they'd be the same see, because they were just that much after me, and - er - then they went out when they - er - got .....

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They went into domestic service as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - yes they did - wait a minute - they wen
t - they both went into the nursing thing in the 1914-18 war - they went as voluntary, you know, whatever they call it in the Red Cross and St. Johns. Yes. Yes, they both went into that and before that I think they'd done a bit of children nursing or some
thing of that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 All three of you were expected to do the same things in the home were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, we were all brought up as a family and all ..... yes. All did the same sort of thing. Each person - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did the older children -
 that would be you and your middle sister - help the younger one with anything she found difficult like dressing or eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Shouldn't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did the younger children help you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh, I expect so, but I can't remember - we weren't allowed up late I know that but I don't know about a certain time - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, I suppose so in the early days - I expect they did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Have you any idea at what age you could put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you share the bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. I had the third room on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think you said you had three bedrooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your parents had one room and two sisters had the other one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 The other two had the other one yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In front of the kitchen fire when we were that age. We'd no bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How often would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh, I couldn't tell you. Forgotten that long ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember when you had clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect we did, I don't remember, I know we were always clean and clothed but I don't remember any set pattern - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would it be a particular night of the week or would you have clean clothes on Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We probably changed more often than that but I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In the kitchen as we called it in those days - in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, in the - in the front sitting room, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would that be if a guest came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes - birthdays and parties and that sort of thing - we had the two rooms - we used to use the two rooms but we
 usually ate in the back one because it was nearer the - um - cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And your mother cooked in the - would that be the back room or the scullery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We had a gas stove in the scullery but we also had in the - about that period that you're talking
 about - um - a kitchen - it wasn't a kitchener, but it was a kitchen grate with an oven and she used to like the kitchen oven for cooking in. But she had a gas stove as well as - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3935796\charrsid1707216 yes}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you remember when you had breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, now, I should imagine - I don't know - I should imagine it would be about eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would all the members of the family be present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your father wouldn't have gone by that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My father used to go at six and come back I think 
about a quarter past eight. Came back and had about half an hour I think for breakfast and then back again - yes. 'Cos he used to go off early about six in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Can you remember what you usually had to eat and drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect it was milk or tea and porridge - I know we always had porridge Quaker oats and that sort of thing - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have a cooked breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I shouldn't think so. I think - er - bread and butter and marmalade I should think because it - everything we had in
 those days was home made - the jam, the marmalade and everything was home made, but - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have anything different on different days, such as Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Can't remember. Its too far back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have a special mid-day meal on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No, I don't think so because we had a good mid-day meal every day. We didn't have an awful lot of meat - we were none of us big meat eaters - my father was a small meat eater and - er - as I say he had the allotment in Pewley Way and we always ha
d about three vegetables - three - every day I mean and - er - that was our - er - chief thing I think was - home grown vegetable and we had some fruit - I think we had some gooseberries and blackberries or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 This would be in the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. He used to use the garden as well as but - er - vegetables, small back garden - he used to use that for vegetables.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have a special tea on Sundays? Or would you eat it in the front room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Probably sometimes but I don't remember anything in particular about that - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about evening meals - as you had a good mid-day meal every day .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We always had tea as far as I can remember between five and six, I think my father used to come home at six. I can't remember wh
ether we waited until he came home but probably we did. But we always had bread and butter, jam and cake - that sort of thing - home made - yes. And home made jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would you have a drink before you went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so. I don't remember, but I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother or father bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But she made her jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 She made her jam and her cakes and her puddings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about bottling fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she ever bottle vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, she didn't - we always had enough to keep us supplied fresh. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
She did - but we weren't a very pickly family - she used to do pickled onions and my father liked pickled onions but she didn't do a lot of pickles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she ever do any home made wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Orange and elderberry and parsnip.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about home made medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was any beer brewed for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You said they did grow their own vegetables and fruit - would they have to buy any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
I don't think so. I can't remember them buying any - we had enough potatoes to last us round until the - next time and - er - the other vegetables I think they kept, you know, one after the other in rotation and we had - I never remember them buying any.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember ever having tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did they keep any livestock for the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When we were very small we had some bantams. In the - the garden at home - yes. At the bottom of the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You didn't have any pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And who would look after the bantams?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh my father would I expect. We were quite small when that happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You said you were small meat eaters but would you have meat most days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or only certain days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, I think we had meat every day but we were not big meat eaters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. They would have been horrified.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever get some extra meat like rabbit from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father have a larger helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, no. He was a small eater for a man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we had to eat what we were given - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well we weren't allowed to unless we weren't well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wait until it was offered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, we were brought up to help ourselves or ask for it if we couldn't reach it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Properly - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When could you leave the table?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When everybody had finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have grace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - yes, I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And that would be said for the whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 For the whole family - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did all the family sit at the table for the main meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you always sit in the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Mmm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How was the meal served - by whom would it be served?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 By my mother I think, usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What order were you served in? Would your father come first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so - I couldn't tell you - sure he would be first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did your younger sisters sit before they could feed themselves? Do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. We had a high chair but I don't remember what happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would your mother feed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember what sort of age they would be when they could join in with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she show affection to her children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about your father - was he easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. He was a very reserved man but he was easy to talk to - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And did he show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, very interested in his family - loved them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you ever share your worries with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, we did - as a family we shared with each other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well that's difficult to answer, I mean, we were brought up to respect and love our parents and we did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so, I don't remember anything like that, I mean, we were al
l brought up to be kind to each other and to - er - help each other and that sort of thing but I don't remember any special er - things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Er - well - er - people who do the right sort of thing - live the right sort of life and - er - see things a way they had brought us up to - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What kind of things would they consider particularly important? You mentioned things such as treating them with respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Oh yes, treating elder people with respect and always speaking the truth and helping anybody that you could and doing anything that you could in the way of being kind and 
helpful - I think that was the - and behaving decently always - yes - I think that was the basic - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I never heard my father swear. He might have said damn once or twice but I never heard him - er - swear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you did something that your parents disapproved of - what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, I expect we should be just gently told off or - er - put right but - er - I don't think anything more than that happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you were punished by whom would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well, we weren't punished as a rule, I mean, we - er - my - my mother used to say we were naughty but - er - I don't know what you'd call naughty today. No we were never r
eally punished. We might - we might get sent to bed if we - er - done something we shouldn't have done - had to go to bed early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your mother took the initiative there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or how you felt about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. We had a very happy childhood really. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Would you say you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I think both were equal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes - they had a little party - party yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have some presents?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, we nearly always had some presents of sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would your mother cook you something special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 A birthday cake or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so. I don't remember, I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And you'd have some friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - no - I think we had the usual Christmas sort of family - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. We used to go to Sunday school or church whatever it was in the morning and I think if I remember we always had a little
 Christmas tree - but - um - we were just the family as far as I remember - we had a Christmas pudding and all the accessories and that sort of thing you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, not - er - I mean - not - not out of the ordinary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - we used to make a row when we sang together I suppose but - er - we didn't do anything ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You didn't sing hymns or songs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We might have done, but I've forgotten now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, when we were very young - but I can't tell you what they played now - but we had ludo, snak
es and ladders and all those sort of things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you ever go out and play games outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
We weren't allowed to play in the streets. My mother used to meet us when we came from school in the summer time - we used to go on Fork Road where you ar
e now because it was fields then and up on Pewley Downs but we were never allowed to play in the streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would your parents go with you if you went up to play there or would you go on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh mother used to go up with us. We never went - I
 don't think we ever went out on our own - we probably played in the back garden but we never - er - you know played anything out in the roads.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think you said your father was fond of reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Very fond - he was a great reader.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there books in the house then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We had a newspapers every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Any magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - not that I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember your mother reading as well as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 She did when she had time - but with three children and - er - father - she didn't have an awful lot of time. But she liked reading.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did they ever read aloud to you or each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, not until my - father
 died - my father's brother died. That was some years before he died and the first - that was the first funeral in the family and the next was my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That would be after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes. Oh that's - yes - in the 20's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you taken out as a child visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. We didn't do a lot of visiting ever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - we used to go round the shops at Christmas time and look at the decorated shops and that - and do that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you got, for instance - shoes - would you go and shop with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, I expect - oh no - I expect we went to the shops with her but - er - I - I really don't remember details about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you did go shopping do you feel it would be with your mother rather than your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Oh yes. Oh yes. My father never did shopping - he never shopped for himself I don't think. I think mother did his shopping, you know, shirts and what not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not in that period - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember any other outings with your parents? Would you have a special expedition that you used to do-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so. We used to go walking - er - when my father had like Bank holidays off and t
hat - we used to walk a lot - we used to walk out to Blackheath and back and all that sort of thing. But that's the only expeditions we had.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You didn't go by train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There wasn't much money to spend on train in those days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My mother took us once or twice when we were children - yes - she took us on - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - I think we went to Southsea once and to Lancing once but I don't remember very much about either of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember how long you'd be away from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh not very long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would you all go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My father didn't go. My mother took the three of us - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember what you did there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Play on the beach and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect we did what the children usually did but I don't remember in the least bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My father used to be in the allotments on Saturday afternoon - I think he used t
o work Saturday morning and - er - in the summer time we used to go up here }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3935796\charrsid1707216 to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
 the allotments and spend the afternoon - and very often take tea up there, you know. But - we didn't do anything special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have your regular jobs to help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about Sundays - what sort of pattern would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we used to go to Sunday school morning and afternoon and church in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So there wasn't very much time left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. There wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have different clothes on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, we always had Sunday clothes and weekday clothes in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, if we wanted to, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So your parents didn't think it was wrong to play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they have thought it wrong to work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well I don't know - I never had anything in that particular line - I mean - they did their normal chores so to speak but - er - well .....

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your father didn't have to work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 He didn't work - no. He probably went up to the allotment, I don't know, but he probably did, that was ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - my father new - in those days didn't - but 
before we were born anyway - he used to go to Stow Church but my mother always came up here - we had the church here where these flats are in those days you know. That's right - she used to come up there - er - regularly with us - yes. But my - er -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That was Anglican Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That's right. Belongs to Holy Trinity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So your mother would come and would this be the Sunday school that you would attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 By that time your father wouldn't come regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, he didn't go not in then - that - latter years - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - yes I think we used to go in the river on a barge if I remember rightly - I think that used to be a Sunday school outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Once a year I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. But that was all - I can't remember - it's very dim that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What other activities might be organized by this ......?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Band of Hope. Yes. Belonged to that. I belonged to that - yes - the Girls Friendly Society - but I didn't belong to that. I didn't do much
 at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would the Band of Hope do? Did they meet regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Yes, I think - I can't tell you how often - but it was regularly - whether it was once a week, once a fortnight I can't remember. We used to do the usual things - songs and games and hymns and all that sort of thing - singing and - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they all be young people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. Oh yes, it was for Sunday school people - well, you know, what we call teenagers in these days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did the church at that time run any temperance club? Band of Hope was that wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well - that was, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That would be the main one would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, there was no temperance club belonging - not to this church anyway. No, the Band of Hope was the temperance society so to speak.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you belong to any other club organized by the church?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No. I don't think there was anything much in those days - there was no youth club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think I asked you before about grace being said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, you did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would it be your father or your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My mother I should imagine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - if we did I can't remember it. We mi
ght have done when we were younger but I don't remember it. We always taught to say our own prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 He was a Liberal - a very strong one. Er - Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Looking back - why do you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Why do I think he did? Oh I don't know - there was only Liberal and - er - Conservative in those days wasn't there and - er - yes there was no Labour back in those days. And Mr Gladstone was his - er - pet man - and we were very keen on 
Mr Gladstone when we were very young - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about your mother - would she be interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - well in latter years she joined the local Conservative party but I don't remember what happened in those years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think she would have the same views as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember your father or mother voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think they would vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think they would vote Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well my father would I know - but I wouldn't know about my mother - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers - do you know if your father felt himself under any kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't know - he never discussed that sort of thing with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was your father a member of the Liberal party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That I don't - that I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would he work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Not as far as I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Nor your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Heavens above - they had no time - 
my father spent his time reading or in the garden - in the allotment and my mother was always busy - a womans work is never done - when she's got a family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Mothers union - that's the only thing I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When did your father get home from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 About six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Every. Yes. Never went out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father attend any clubs? Or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your mother go to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did he ever go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs - like a boot club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well he used to belong to slate club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think it was the co-operative slate club - I'm not sure. I'm not sure but I think it was the co-operative society ran the slate club.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did they belong to a funeral club or a sick club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Um - well that would be it - that would be it - yes - that would be for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did you get on with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there one you felt particularly close to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 As a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well - school pals of my own age I suppose and my sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And you told me you played either in your own garden or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Up on Powley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you ever go into the other childrens gardens? Or other homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh, I expect we did - though I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And I think you said you played ludo and snakes and ladders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes - all those sort of things indoors - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh well of course we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not that I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they get cross if you got dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You said you belonged to the Band of Hope which was a sort of youth temperance club - did you belong to any other youth organisation?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - used to knit and crochet and sew but - er - I don't remember doing anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Crest china at one time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No. Um - no we never had a cat or - they had a dog when I was born I think but it - er - jealous and they got rid of it and don't think we ever had a pet after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you went up to the allotment would you ever do any of the gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, no. We used to play around - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You said you went for walks to Blackheath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15366769\charrsid1707216 Yes. St Martha's, N}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 ewlands Corner and all round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you bicycle?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I didn't bicycle then - no - I did in latter years but not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you go to any theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, there wasn't one here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Music-halls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No. There was nothing here then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 About a penny a week I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That would be regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think we had a penny regularly - which we used to split into four farthings and spend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Anything we could get - bullseyes and that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Sweets mainly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Penny - er - farthings worth of this that and the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Had you any relations living near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Not near here - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about if your mother was ill or confined to bed - how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well as far as I remember - er - my father used to - just look after her - probably t
here was a neighbour - I don't - can't remember that, I mean .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about when your sisters were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we had a nurse who used to come in - yes - a monthly nurse who used to come in - we were all born at home - and - um -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And then would she live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No, she didn't live in the house - I don't know what hap - I can't remember what happened about that - probably - she used to come in .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Look after your mother and the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That's right. And whether my father got help I can't remember in the least bit what happened about that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you stay at home when your younger sisters were born or would you go away and stay with somebody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I was a over - I was sent over the road I remember once when one of them was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What to a neighbour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Yes. But I don't remember what happened with the second one - no. Er - no we were always back again after - as soon as things were all right you know. We weren't away from home. And I can't remember - in th
e least remember whether mother had anybody came - whether she had any friends come from away, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Had she got some good neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That she was friendly with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Er - no - I don't think he did many. He had one or two work mates but he hadn't anybody - we hadn't people come to the house or that sort of thing to see him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where would your parents see their friends if they did see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh just normally in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So would they share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But your mother would have friends that your father.....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh - my mother had many - er - most of my mothers friends were not living here, I mean the
y were friends of her earlier days - they used to come and stay with us - I mean we adopted them as aunts you know, but - er - she was friendly with her neighbours but - er - I wouldn't ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would she ever go and stay with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not then. No, not when - not up 'til 1918 - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your father hadn't got similar friends who'd come and stay with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were friends ever invited into the home? Apart from these friends who came to stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh anybody that my mother knew - I mean if she wanted them - well she had them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they just call in to see her or would they be offered a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, if anybody came in and it was mealtime or afternoon cup of tea time she would always be - er - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would there be any particular days or occasions when she'd have her friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you say that the friends invited in were usually your mother's friends or your father's friends or both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, we didn't have a terrific number of friends to come
 in in that sense of the way. As I say my father had no special friends except for a work-mate or two who lived in Guildford but they didn't visit and - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So it sounds as if it would mainly be friends that your mother had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes, it would be but I can't remember an awful lot just about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would friends call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I should imagine so - it was an open house usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 This would apply to neighbours as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. We didn't visit in and 
out and live in other people houses but if anybody came in I mean she made them welcome. We were never used to living in in each others houses - I never remember going in and out of neighbours houses except just to say how do you do can we help you.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well they did, didn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did your parents do together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well there wasn't much th
ey could do together was there - I mean my father was working all day and came home and he was a great book reader - he read. My mother was busy all the time with her needlework and her - there wasn't anything to - no - there was no time to go out and enj
oy themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Many people divide society into different social classes or groups in that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to one group and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so, I mean, you always thought of the wealthy pe
ople as the upper class, but - er - and the working class - I mean that was all there was to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Just the two you felt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You would be conscious of an upper class group and .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 A working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 A working class group. Would you say that your family belonged to the working class group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 The working class group - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What sort of people would belong to this group as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, any ordinary family of those times - yes - were working class people weren't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 The people living round you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Yes. Yes. I mean everybody was working for their living in those days except the as we call them - upper class here - who were more or less the retired people who were living in the bigger houses round about here, you know, I mean ....
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And who would be the upper class group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well that's what I say - it would be the people living in the bigger houses round here that would ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And what would they .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well it might be Army, Navy - um - doctors or 
- um - people with a little more money. I mean, round this particular area they were mostly retired service people and that type of person I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If a doctor was still working and practicing what sort of group would he be in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well I imagine 
he would be sort of upper working class perhaps - I don't know, but I don't know what the definition would be in those days for in between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you feel that the doctor who was still working would be in the same sort of grouping as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 O
h he'd be a bit superior we should feel because the education would be a bit better wouldn't it - I mean that would be the idea. He'd have had a bigger education than the ordinary working class children would get, I mean, not like today when they can go a
broad and all that sort of thing, we just - we learnt reading, writing and arithmetic and - um - the three R's and needlework and that sort of thing but I mean we didn't have the chances that children have got today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one group differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you ever told to curtsy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there anyone you called Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well - anybody we didn't know - or didn'
t know their name or anything - you would normally or naturally say good afternoon Sir or Madam. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And if you knew their name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You'd call them by it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh most people did that k
new them. I mean, people that - people that - er - my father and my mother both commanded respect as far as that went, you know, whether they were known or not known.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would anybody call them Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Strangers probably would. I think it was the thing in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In this area of Charlotteville who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well it was a working class area.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you conscious of important people living round about - they weren't actually in the area?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Um - no, I wouldn't - I wouldn't know of anyone in particular, I mean there were doctors living outside and there were retired as I say living around and that - you knew th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15366769\charrsid1707216 
em by sight - you knew them by n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 ame - but - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There were a lot of retired people living in Guildford in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes. All round Harvey Road and that way and Epsom Road and .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - not a lot - not in early days anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about the shopkeepers - who did they associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about clergy - where would they come in this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well we - we were in Holy Trinity parish here - and of course the clergy used to visit more then than they do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they be considered upper class or working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't know - that's a bit difficult to answer isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would teachers come into a different category?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well I suppose you'd look on them as superior people because they were educating you more or less sort of thing wouldn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you know any farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or employers of business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You went to Charlotteville church would the people there be much the same social grouping as your own family? Or would they be different?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Charlotteville church? St Lukes Church. They were all our equals. Yes. All the same type of person - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would it be different at Holy Trinity - would you know anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, Holy Trinity in those days I think was mostly the Congregationa
l - the biggest part of it - were the people who lived in the High Street - the trades-people and - and the people round about well from what was Warwicks Bench and - er - round about these roads here - Harvey Road - they were the biggest part of the Cong
r
egation. We had an odd person or two used to come to St Lukes - um - the Miss Lesters who lived in Semaphore House - they used to come - do you remember them, no I don't suppose you do. And - er - Miss Kings - the dentists daughter they used to come up - 
people like that used to come up but they were mostly Holy Trinity congregation - we were the daughter church of Holy Trinity, you see. And it was for the people of this end - the church was in use.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you know anybody who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - well yes, I suppose I did, but I can't remember them off hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they be - as far as the social groupings go - would they be any different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about Roman Catholics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Don't know anybody.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There was no friction with Roman Catholics in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Where you lived did all the people in the working class group have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups within the group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh there wer
e probably different groups within the groups, I mean, - um - and maybe more the - what shall I say - the sort of labouring class the same as there are now I presume, you know, like the labourers and those sort of things, but I couldn't tell you anything 
about that as I mean I'm afraid I wasn't interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They were unskilled people you would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so. I should imagine so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would they be thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so, not particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 A family in the same sort of group as yourself - would you think of them as being in a job which required more skill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so. I mean the people we knew were much about - well they were like railway people or people of that sort of thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But your father was quite skilled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Oh he was a skilled - yes, he was skilled - worker - well so of course were the train drivers and those sort of people, I mean, there were people of that category living around - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So many of them would be skilled in their work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, yes, in their own work - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well I think when we were that age we never troubled about that sort of thing. I mean we didn't bother our heads about whether one group was - or we were grouped or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think this was because you were a young child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 It was - it didn't worry us - no - we weren't interested. No, we weren't interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would you know some families who would be thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh well there's always one or two rough people about isn't there - er - still are but - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you remember a distinction of this sort between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your father and mother have the same attitude to people in different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was it possible at that time to move from one group to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I wouldn't know - I wouldn't know anything about that sort of thing - I mean we just weren't interested in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, People used to say oh well that's a real gentleman or a real lady.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would they mean by it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well I think mannerisms and - er - that sort of thing. Chiefly mannerisms as much as anything I think, I mean, people wouldn't think of pushing you
 off the pavement or - they'd get off or they'd raise their hat to you - where these days they don't even bother to make way for you - I think that would be the sort of - oh he's a real - yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Behaving in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes. Yes, 
you didn't need to have money to be a real gentleman. People would said oh hes a born gentleman or she's a born lady - which is - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 From the way they behaved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, they used to come round occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Didn't worry about him I don't think. Never thought ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you were naughty did your mother say I'll send for a policeman? No? How do you think he treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No idea. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, he used to come round every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh he was all right. He was all right to get on with. We used to
 think he was a bit mean sometimes when he wouldn't do anything. But he was all right, I mean, as a landlord he was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember feeling your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well of course there were times because I mean
 things weren't always - especially during the - the er - war - things were a bit difficult on their small money that they had in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were you aware of it as a child - did it over concern you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so, I mean, my mother might sa
y oh well I want so and so or fetch - er - buy so and so but don't give more than so and so because I can't afford it. That sort of thing but we were never made aware that they - er - were struggling. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So you didn't feel anxiety?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We weren't - it wasn't sort of - put to us that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was your father ever ill? And out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 He - once or twice he had bouts of got I think but I don't think he - I don't remember him being ill apart from that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What difference would that make to the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What, being out of work? There was no money coming in - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So do you remember any feeling of anxiety when he was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Oh no, not at that age I don't remember anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your family ever get any help from the Guardians or the Parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How many servants were there in the job you had at St. Catherines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I couldn't tell you now - there was a kitchen maid ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. There were people in the kitchen, there were people in the still room, there were materns - there were housemaids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Quite a big group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. I can't remember how many now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And you were a housemaid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have special servants quarters to live in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we had a servants hall, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where abouts did you sleep - did you have a house of your own or did you sleep in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, no, the - all the staff rooms were in the school, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Where did you sit when you were not working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In the servants hall - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was that reasonably comfortable? Or was it just like a dining hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. No, it was a - it was a sitting room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well equipped?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you know any members of the staff apart from your colleagues?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
We knew all the mistresses and that sort of thing - oh yes. Yes. Because you - well it was all in the work - you knew everybody. You didn't know the pupils - I mean - not all the pupils, but you knew the staff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you get to know a few of the senior pupils?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh not to - sort of - you knew them but not to have anything to do with them - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did you get on with the other domestic staff? Was that a happy group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you enjoy the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever wish you were doing something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Who would be your immediate supervisor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Mrs Russell Baker was the head of the St Catherines school in those days - she was the one who - interviewed everybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And then who would supervise your work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh the matrons. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would they give any sort of guidance to you as to what you wore or how you spent you money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Good gracious - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You were left completely free?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 To do what you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would you do when you were not working in the school - if you were indoors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well you were doing normal things in those days, I mean, sew, knit, read or something like this, I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Altogether?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Altogether or in your own room - which you liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Your room was sufficiently comfortable to be able to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well it was an ordinary bedroom - I think two of us shared or three of us shared, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What sort of time off did you have - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we had a half day a week and a half day on Sunday I think, as far as I remember
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And did you usually go home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Didn't you say there weren't any buses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. I walked - from Bramley to Guildford and back again. Yes. Walked all my life - all my early life - there were no buses in Guildford.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would you walk back in the dark?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 My father walked back with me in the winter time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And then back again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - yes. I think on a Sunday he would get a train back at nine o'clock but there was nothing out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever feel homesick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I expect so - I don't know - don't remember that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember enjoying the company of the other staff or did you feel lonely sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Oh I don't think so because you had your own friends and you - and then you were in and out and my own home was here and you were never lonely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would your sisters have gone by this time to nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no. They were still at school and, I mean, t
here's nearly four years difference between myself and my younger sister. I'm the eldest - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there anything you particularly liked or disliked about the job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You were quite happy there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What sort of time did you have your meals, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, I couldn't remember that - you're joking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have a very early breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What was the food like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh the normal food of those days - we had - er - plenty of good plain food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would it be much the same as the .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Exactly the same as the school - oh yes - the whole thing was right through - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Before you went to school did your parents begin to teach you anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Which school did you go to first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Charolotteville board school - first and last. Charlotteville board school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Right through?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Right through.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember what sort of hours schooling they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes - we were from nine 'til twelve and again from two 'til four or half past, I don't remember exactly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you go home to lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So you weren't very far from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not a great way - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. There was no other way to getting there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And it would take you ten minutes or a quarter of an hour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I expect so - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was it boys as well as girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - no. It was separate in the time that I was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Just girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. The boys were at the
 top end - Pewley Way - what is Pewley school now. That was the boys school then - and the girls were down in Sydenham Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Before your sisters were old enough to go to school did you go by yourself or did someone go with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Haven't the foggiest idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember what you thought of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. I always enjoyed it but I don't know any more than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You enjoyed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did you feel about the teachers? Do you remember what you felt about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No. I don't think it worried us very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think the teachers emphasised certain things as important in life like manners and tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect they did but I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't know - I expect we got lines to write or something but I can't remember that far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would there be any severe punishments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh they were always interested in what we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 In those days did parents visit the school and meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I don't ever remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did the other children come from similar types of homes to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember if the teachers ever singled out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. Don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there any groups in the school that kept together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Not to my knowledge. Don't remember anything of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember any children who seemed to be left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No, I can't remember any of those little details I'm afraid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Between fourteen and fifteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity or were you glad to leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Er - I don't know - probably would have stayed longer if there'd been the opportunity.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any part time education afterwards? Evening classes or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I went for a short time but - er - to a Technical College but not for very long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What sort of subjects were you studying there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well I was taking - going in for typing and shorthand but - er - at the time I wasn't very strong and they did
n't think office work or that sort of thing was suitable and I had to have something more active. That was one reason why I think I was sent into domestic service because it was better than office work or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I suppose in those days it was not so usual to do shorthand and typing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
No, and there was very little here apart from domestic service or the shops. Just the ordinary shops you know, there was no offices much or anything of that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you regret that you weren't able to do the office work - would you have preferred that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well, I don't know - the only thing I regret now is that we hadn't the opportunities the present day people have got because we would have made use of them. We'd got the brains but there wasn't the opportunity to develop them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I don't know - I don't know that I use it much. Do you mean evening classes or .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I was thinking of school generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh school generally - well we - I suppose it did - I could read, write and - and do all the - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3935796\charrsid1707216 arithmetic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216  and that sort of thing. I mean, I left in the X seventh so I must have been fairly brilliant but - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could you tell me how the forms went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They went from one to seven I think - as far as I remember - yes. One, two infants and then sort of gradually go up I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would each number be split into different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We had different class rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So when you said you were X seven - what would that mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well, I - don't know - I don't remember what that meant - I suppose really we got some extra lessons or hard lessons or something - we passed the seventh standard which was the top standard and were ......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So that would perhaps be a group of the brighter girls at the top of the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Brighter girls - probably would in these days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 While you were still at school did you do any part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 After you left St Catherines you went to a family didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I went down to Liss - to a ferrymans family - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did you hear of that job - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh Yes - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3935796\charrsid1707216 through}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216  some people that my mother knew.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And what exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well I did housework - parlourwork there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What hours did you work - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well we worked all hours of the days in those days - yes. I mean to say there was no sort of, as you must know yourself, there's no sort of definite hours in housework or running a house is there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But I was wondering what the pattern of the family was - whether you had to get up very early to get them breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no. I think we were down about seven or something like that but I really can't remember - I don't think we were down before se
ven - and breakfast I think was about nine o'clock for the family and ours was eight o'clock I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there any other staff apart from yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There was the cook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Just the two of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have free time on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would that be part of a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, part of the day. A morning one week and afternoon the other and we took it in turns - you know - alternately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 That wouldn't give you time to come home would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh not from Liss, no, no. If I came home I had the whole day off but I can't tell you how often I did that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you have any time off on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no. Not - er - nothing definite - there was a half day in the week, sort of thing, but I mean - er - t
here was no - not like they do today - kind of business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes - a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You don't remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No - I can't remember - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you remember if you felt it was a reasonable salary for the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
Well I don't think we worried about those things in those days, I don't know, I mean I think when I went to Liss I had twenty pound a year as far as I can remember and that was quite a - a start off - and - er - yes - but I don't t
hink we ever went into it like they do today - oh we must have more money and we must get more money and that sort of thing - it was left to ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did you get on with your employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you feel that they took an interest in you as a person?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They did - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about the work - how did you like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well it was the work that I was used to more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you quite enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you give any of the money that you had to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, I had to in those days because my father's health was cracking then and his work was getting slack.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would she use it for the general housekeeping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 She used - it for the home to supplement....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you dress yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You would pay for your own clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes - everything - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about the cook - how did you get on with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Very well - she was much older. She was much older than I was but she was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You liked working with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did you do in your spare time? You said you always came home from Bramley - would you always come home from Liss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no. I - er - well I had - made friends with the 
girl who married when I took her job on and - er - I used to go to her home and we used to walk and I learnt to bicycle while I was down there, we used to ride and walk, that we was our chief interests.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 It was rather nice having somebody that you got to know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes, it took me an hour to get home by train - I couldn't have come home in a half day or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she have a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. She's still alive today and we're still friends. But she's - she must be about eighty-six now I think because she's a good bit .....

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Does she still live down there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, she's still down there. Yes. That was her home - she was born and bred there and her husband too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you ever bring her home to your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, lots of times.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any boyfriends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I wondered if you met any down there in Liss.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh I met lots down there different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would there be to do with any other friends that you met?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There was nothing 
but walk or - er - have tea - you know - go to their homes and have tea - that sort of thing - er - no clubs or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No dances or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, nothing of that sort in the village - no - nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 It would be quite countrified Liss wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh it would - it was quite a village - yes. No lights - no nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
When you were at the school at Bramley could you tell me what sort of time table it would be on Sundays? Would you have to do much the same sort of work as you did other days or would it be different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I should imagine it was about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 You wouldn't have a slacker day on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well, we - er - there again we had one Sunday morning one week - one Sunday afternoon the other so it wouldn't be exactly 
the same as the weekday but I mean there were certain things - er - certain things to do all the time you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What would you do with your half day if you couldn't come home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I always came home. From Bramley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you had Sunday morning off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh - went to church. Yes. Went to Warnash church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Could the staff go to any church they wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They didn't have to go to church of England because St. Catherines is a Church of England School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, yes. Oh no, you weren't forced to go to church anywhere you were free to do as you liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How did the staff behave towards the domestic staff? Did they treat them considerately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there quite a friendly atmosphere throughout the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would the same apply to the girls who had any contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes. Yes, they were all friendly - yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What about the headmistress - did you come in contact with her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh quite a bit - yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you like her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 She was very nice - she was a very stately person but she was very nice - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she take an interest in the staff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 As individuals I mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Of course there must have been quite a lot of people under her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh there were - can't tell you how many but there were a lot of mistresses and I think over a hundred girl boarders in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Were there day children then as well as boarders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 It was quite a big set-up then really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes - it was - not so big as it is today - but it was a big set-up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents ever visit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What did you wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 What do you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have a special housemaid's uniform?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we just had cotton frocks for working in the morning and - er - black frock and a fancy apron in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did the school supply that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh no, we had to buy those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 They would pay for laundering and so on would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you feel that your job at the school changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you meet people of a sort you hadn't met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you feel that the teachers you met were different in any way from the ones you'd met at school for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you came home did you spend your free time differently from how you had done before or did you carry on much the same pattern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Well there wasn't an awful lot of time. By the time you'd walked home from Bram
ley to Guildford it was mid afternoon - by the time you'd had some tea and started to walk back again it wasn't - there wasn't much time to do anything but just be at home.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And I suppose in those days families just sat around and talked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, o
r if you wanted to do any shopping you had to do your shopping in that time - I mean there wasn't an awful lot of time to do anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you make any different friends at home while you were at the Bramley job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you keep up with any of your old school friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 One. And she died two years ago in Canada. That was the only one - and we kept up 'til now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 How long had she been in Canada?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I think she went out in 1923 - I think - as far as I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did she come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, she never came home - no. We corresponded the whole time - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So one can keep friends by correspondence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh you can - yes, yes. I don't think they ever made enough money - or her husband never made enough money to come home but - 
er - of course he died some years back and she lived on her own in a flat until - I think it was about two years - somewhere along now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 When you started full time work did you feel that it changed your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Or with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 If you came home on a Sunday afternoon would you continue to go to the same church or whatever you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did your parents meet your Guildford friends - if you met your - for instance - the frien
d you've just been telling me about - would she come to your house or would you go to her house or would you meet somewhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 We did both. For a short time she lived next door to us - long - long after I met her first - but then - er - after that
 the family moved out to Peasmarsh - but er - we exchanged houses - parties and all that sort of thing. When I first about twelve - we were about twelve years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So that was really your main friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Did you have any other friends that you used to go and visit in their homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we had several school pals round about here that we used to go to and they to us sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Was there anything much to do if you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No, only walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 There wouldn't be any concerts or anything like that to go to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
I don't remember anything in that line - no - we had the Band of Hope - the Band of Hope concerts and that sort of thing but apart from that I mean there were no public things that we went to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Would you be able to continue to go to the Band of Hope after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I didn't. No, you couldn't. Well, you can't when you .......
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Because that would be a week night wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Yes, that's right. You can't when you're - er -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 But could you go to any special sort of thing they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Never bothered after I once left it - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And you did say you didn't take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think that if you had you would have felt more sympathetic towards the Liberals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
We were a Liberal family - in those days - yes. My father was a great what you call - Gladstonian. Mr Gladsone was his - er - chief - um - example shall I say - put it that way and Lloyd George he was quite in touch with I mean he quite agreed wi
th lots of his things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you thin you would have felt the same sort of sympathy as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Oh we were - no we were brought up to his way of thinking. But we didn't worry about politics I'm afraid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Of course you wouldn't have a vote would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 So it didn't come to the point of having to decide?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. We weren't - no - we weren't interested in politics in those days - not to that extent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 Do you think that most of the young people like yourself that you met weren't interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No. No, I don't think so. I don't remember anybody ever talking about politics in those days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 And would this be the same when you went out to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 As far as I remember - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I wouldn't be discussed there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 People just weren't interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13897206 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 I suppose they weren't involved?
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid13897206 \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11680730 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9113725\charrsid1707216 
They weren't interested. No. See no one had the vote until they were twenty one in any case, so it wouldn't matter what you were interested in - it didn't matter - you had no say in the matter in any case.
\par }}